The 1999 offering from the crew at Lost. Over two years in the making. This is Volume One in a series of videos which will be loosely based on covering American surf spots and their surfers. There are hundreds of cities and thousands of spots. Much of this movie is made up of home footage supplied by local surfers from around the country. The rest was shot by professionals, in and out of the water.
